description: Try our easy to follow Roast Vegetable Frittata recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Roast Vegetable Frittata Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.75 cup vitamin D fortified soy milk

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk eggs and milk in a bowl. Season to taste. Stir in half of the spinach and half of the feta. Pour over vegetables and gently stir to combine. Bake for 30-35 minutes or until set and golden. Serve with remaining spinach and feta and crusty bread.
